<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">2024年12月4日</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">是我国第十一个国家宪法日</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">12月1日至12月7日</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">是第七个“宪法宣传周”</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">今年“宪法宣传周”主题为</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">大力弘扬宪法精神</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">推动进一步全面深化改革</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">宪法是国家的根本大法，是治国安邦的总章程，适用于国家全体公民，学习宪法对民众具有重要的现实意义，那么宪法究竟与你我的一生如何息息相关呢？一起来看看！</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241207/1733549006611020204.jpg" title="1733549006611020204.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241206145118.jpg" width="684" height="757" style="width: 684px; height: 757px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241207/1733549021016055232.jpg" title="1733549021016055232.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241206145123.jpg" width="686" height="1315" style="width: 686px; height: 1315px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241207/1733549034189015027.jpg" title="1733549034189015027.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241206145128.jpg" width="688" height="1615" style="width: 688px; height: 1615px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241207/1733549055353053161.jpg" title="1733549055353053161.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241206145132.jpg" width="684" height="1484" style="width: 684px; height: 1484px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241207/1733549071377069050.jpg" title="1733549071377069050.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241206145137.jpg" width="687" height="1337" style="width: 687px; height: 1337px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241207/1733549083161019652.jpg" title="1733549083161019652.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241206145143.jpg" width="686" height="1198" style="width: 686px; height: 1198px;"/></span></p><p><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>